          <h1 class="readme-h1">Hi, I'm Sayan Ghosh 👋</h1>

          <p class="readme-p">
            <span class="badge green">✓ Open to opportunities</span>
            <span class="badge blue">VP @ JP Morgan &amp; Chase</span>
            <span class="badge purple">ML/AI Product</span>
            <span class="badge orange">15+ years exp</span>
          </p>

          <p class="readme-p">ML/AI Product Leader with 7+ years of product management and 15+ years overall experience building and scaling intelligent data platforms across <strong>financial services</strong>, <strong>energy</strong>, and <strong>manufacturing</strong>. Proven track record defining product vision and delivering ML/AI solutions that automate complex workflows and drive measurable efficiency gains.</p>

          <div class="highlight-box">
            💡 Certified Agile Delivery Lead (PSM, SAFe 5) recognized for driving innovation, accelerating time-to-value, and delivering enterprise-scale impact in regulated environments.
          </div>

          <h2 class="readme-h2">⚡ Impact Highlights</h2>

          <div style="margin-bottom:8px;">
            <div class="readme-li">Reduced commercial client onboarding from <code class="inline">7 days → 3 days</code> (57% faster) for 10K cases/year via ML-driven API solutions</div>
            <div class="readme-li">Achieved <code class="inline">95% operational efficiency</code> (40h → 2h) through ML/rule-driven decisioning on client assessment platform</div>
            <div class="readme-li">Delivered DCB Insights framework with 3 pilot insights in 9 months, enabling 75% of targeted MVP use cases for 100+ clients</div>
            <div class="readme-li">Led a team of <code class="inline">2 product analysts + 18 engineers</code> across Commercial & Investment Banking data products</div>
            <div class="readme-li">3× Capgemini Customer Delight Award winner for cloud delivery excellence (2019, 2020, 2021)</div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="readme-h2">🛠 What I Build</h2>
          <div style="margin-bottom:8px;">
            <div class="readme-li">ML/AI platforms for <strong>document intelligence</strong>, <strong>entity resolution</strong>, and <strong>risk scoring</strong></div>
            <div class="readme-li">End-to-end KYC/KYB/AML/CDD compliance automation systems</div>
            <div class="readme-li">Real-time API data products for front &amp; middle office banking workflows</div>
            <div class="readme-li">Microservice architectures on AWS, GCP, and Cloud Foundry/Predix</div>
            <div class="readme-li">Industrial IoT platforms with predictive modeling for energy &amp; manufacturing</div>
          </div>

